asset_contract.description:
Fresh Fools is a 5757 NFT Collection, by a group of real life friends, who decided to work together to make the Fools a real thing.
Each Fresh Fool will reside on the Ethereum blockchain as a unique NFT, made of a unique combination of hand-drawn traits that set them apart. Owning a Fresh Fool will not only make you more foolish, but will allow you to vote and participate on community-driven features, products and online events. This makes our roadmap cooperative and will allow Fool holders to help the founders decide on it, including how we spend our community wallet.

asset_contract.name: IFICE
asset_contract.description:
IFICE is made up of 6884 unique frames, with each image derived from 22 larger sequences. Digital artifices and memories shared amongst collectors

Each IFICE token serves as a ticket that can only ever be claimed once. Claiming enables access to a digital viewing room to experience a short montage that connects every frame of a ticket's associated sequence.

After this single viewing, the ticket survives as a standalone artwork. It persists as a memento experentia, a fully tradable souvenir of a past experience. A lost frame in time.
